      "content": "\"optimization exercise\"... that's a pretty big stretch if a tech journalist actually asks for details. If they dig and find out it was just an S3 bucket left open, aren't we going to look even worse for being dishonest? Is there a way to frame it that isn't quite so... misleading, but still avoids the word \"leak\"?",
